#. <section class="sutta" id="sn3.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.23:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Tatiyavagga"
msgstr "3. Kosala"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Lokasutta"
msgstr "23. The World"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.98"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.219"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.23:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, King Pasenadi said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.3"
msgid ""
"“kati nu kho, bhante, lokassa dhammā uppajjamānā uppajjanti ahitāya dukkhāya "
"aphāsuvihārāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, how many things arise in the world for its harm, suffering, and "
"discomfort?”"

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Tayo kho, mahārāja, lokassa dhammā uppajjamānā uppajjanti ahitāya dukkhāya "
"aphāsuvihārāya."
msgstr ""
"“Great king, three things arise in the world for its harm, suffering, and "
"discomfort."

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.5"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.6"
msgid ""
"Lobho kho, mahārāja, lokassa dhammo, uppajjamāno uppajjati ahitāya dukkhāya "
"aphāsuvihārāya."
msgstr "Greed,"

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.7"
msgid ""
"Doso kho, mahārāja, lokassa dhammo, uppajjamāno uppajjati ahitāya dukkhāya "
"aphāsuvihārāya."
msgstr "hate,"

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.8"
msgid ""
"Moho kho, mahārāja, lokassa dhammo, uppajjamāno uppajjati ahitāya dukkhāya "
"aphāsuvihārāya."
msgstr "and delusion."

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.9"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, mahārāja, tayo lokassa dhammā uppajjamānā uppajjanti ahitāya "
"dukkhāya aphāsuvihārāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These three things arise in the world for its harm, suffering, and "
"discomfort.”"

msgctxt "sn3.23:1.10"
msgid "Idamavoca … pe …"
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. …"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.23:2.1"
msgid "“Lobho doso ca moho ca,"
msgstr "“When greed, hate, and delusion,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.23:2.2"
msgid "purisaṃ pāpacetasaṃ;"
msgstr "have arisen inside oneself,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.23:2.3"
msgid "Hiṃsanti attasambhūtā,"
msgstr "they harm a person of wicked heart,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.23:2.4"
msgid "tacasāraṃva samphalan”ti."
msgstr "as a reed is destroyed by its own fruit.”"
